" placed on top or behind, other images, by default depends on how "
"columns/layers are placed in the Xsheet/Timeline: Xsheet direction is "
"from left to right, while Timeline direction is from bottom to top, "
"making what's on the left/bottom to be behind of what's on the right/top."
