"Xsheet column (or Timeline layer) order is what's taken into account when"
" there are no modifications to the SO position. As soon as a column/layer"
" has a higher SO value, it will be placed on top, regardless of the "
"position of the column/layer in the Xsheet/Timeline; conversely if the SO"
" value is lower it will be placed behind."
