#: ../../source/creating_movements.rst:650
msgid ""
"It's also possible to link the keyframes of the objects to the positions "
"of the control points defining the motion path, so that they remain "
"consistent when the motion path is edited. To help you better understand "
"where the control points are, the object snaps to them when it is dragged"
" along the motion path."
