"When a multiple key is inserted at the current frame, a key is created "
"for each Xsheet column (or Timeline layer) where an animation level is "
"exposed; if a column/layer selection is defined, keys are created in "
"selected columns/layers only (see  :ref:`Working with Xsheet Columns "
"<working_with_xsheet_columns>`  )."
