#: ../../source/creating_movements.rst:842
msgid ""
"When a multiple key is deleted at the current frame, any key available in"
" any Xsheet column (or Timeline layer) at the current frame is deleted; "
"if a column/layer selection is defined, keys are deleted in selected "
"columns/layers only."
